  </dt>

  <dd>
    The app uses the device's barometer. For example, a weather app could
    report air pressure.
  </dd>

  <dt>
    <code>android.hardware.sensor.compass</code>
  </dt>

  <dd>
    The app uses the device's magnetometer (compass). For example, a navigation
